<div class="quote-controls"></div>
<img loading="lazy" alt="" width="24" height="24" src="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/e/ba8739/48.png" class="avatar"> etbarbaric:</div>
<blockquote>
<p>I do take the point that something like Vision (a Limelight in our case) doesn’t really <em>need</em> to be a subsystem.</p>
</blockquote>
</aside>
